	<h1>Better Output</h1>

	In the Output example, as Tapestry renders the template it calls <em>getMessage()</em> which generates a value "on the fly".<br/>
	A more usual technique is to set up all property values once, before rendering, in the SetupRender phase.

	<div class="eg">
		${message}<br/>
		${message}<br/>
		${message}
	</div>
	
